Okay, here's a Telugu joke for you:

Teacher: Raju, nuvvu enduku school ki late ga vachavu? (Raju, why did you come late to school?)

Raju: Naaku road mida oka rupayi dorikindi, anduke teacher! (I found a rupee on the road, that's why teacher!)

Teacher: Aite, rupayi dorikithe, thattuga vachiveddam kada? (If you found a rupee, you should have come quickly, right?)

Raju: Sare teacher, malli dorikithe thattuga vastanu! (Okay teacher, if I find another one, I'll come quickly!)

Hope you liked it! Let me know if you want to hear another one.
